Comment: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========正文============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓果然不同凡響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮  羨慕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說要當結婚雜誌的模特兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為我也能穿輕飄飄的可愛衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  對方要求有一個男性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們的事務所又沒人選
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  我要鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這很適合真君呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這條領帶的品味也讓人佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到第一次穿婚紗是工作需要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前覺得自己在此之前就已經結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚慾望很強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總覺得像這樣努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天能遇到我的白馬王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  製作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件禮服馬上就要換掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  午休後就要換別的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是發給朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(60,20)\fs18}「我要奔向幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(135,40)\fs18}真抱歉  其實我下個月28號就要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(83,60)\fs18}雖然說好不會偷跑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(50,80)\fs18}真的很抱歉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣…發送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友美一定會嚇一跳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  友美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用這麼驚訝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算結婚又有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙你的騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實只是結婚雜誌的模特兒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次見面再好好聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該馬上就能請到假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…我什麼時候走到這裡來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  您掉東西…了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  找到新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  回婚禮現場了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…還有攝影…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐到哪裡去打電話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便當都已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是梓小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓…梓小姐被拐走了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我親眼看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是梓的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作人  現在立刻就去救人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希  我們會盡快回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幫我們拖延下時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希我會試試的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明白您不願意和從未相識的人結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們的主人是很了不起的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也一定會滿意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之立刻回到婚禮現場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…請問是不是認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是三浦梓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要穿那麼容易混淆的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了  是結婚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得還給那位新娘才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  工作室那邊也要回去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  我到底是從哪裡過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幹  這種父母間決定的婚事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打死都不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣說  我們主人也是打心底想要娶您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都把先祖代代相傳的傳家寶戒送您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是其證明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種戒指還你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來…剛才那人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯的  是傳家寶戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快回去找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機也掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼去工作室…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  坐計程車就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我想問一下路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我離開村莊來這裡見兒子但卻迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去那個叫Land  Land  Tower的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真對不起  我也在趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你幫忙了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先帶您去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作人  再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別強人所難了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那輛車…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作人  就是那輛車拐走梓小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計程車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請跟著前面那輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是警察什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  把梓小姐帶哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓？是剛才那人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人也在找戒指嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊急聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在車站目擊到穿著婚紗的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解  趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓戒指被搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  誘拐犯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真  很危險的  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請給我發票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標從車站前往中華街
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我也一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話  帶我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉  我忘記自己也是路盲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  我一個人肯定也會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  俊嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  沒迷路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說在那個Land  Land  Tower碰面的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是約好在這個Marine  Port  Tower等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是您帶母親過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡  只是路盲碰巧走對路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你添麻煩了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆也保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也要快點找輛計程車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個孩子的母親在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解  發現後立即確保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息說在肉包子店目擊到那女的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剛才那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不會把梓小姐交給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很燙要當心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  我也想讓她吹吹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去買肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs22}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開  讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那個…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像聽到了真的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來這是幸運肉包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金錢運一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛運馬馬虎虎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找的人在前方3米？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我也該回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是呢  三浦小姐和菊地君都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只剩你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正待會兒也要拍她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三浦回來之前先拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只有這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快點準備一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用著急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在梓她們回來之前  要給美希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認  認錯人了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓  你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不過剛才那人挺帥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥都畫不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼能激發靈感呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈感來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真頭疼啊  哪都找不到計程車站  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  能拜託你看下店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕快點回去工作才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  能幫我占卜一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好  那個  不過可能不準
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好精彩的電影啊  正好到高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個演員  好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實啊  我被跟我有婚約的女士甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天就要離開日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以最後想在日本找一個能留下美好回憶的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該去哪比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個  要怎麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是塔羅牌還能懂一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  萬事試為先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是港口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  我就去看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人只有一個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,費用放在裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是幫大忙了  必須要好好答謝你才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  能告訴我計程車站在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  就這事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個的話  看  在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希個人覺得婚紗再加點躍動感會比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯啊  很新穎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  攝影師  美希突然想在海邊拍攝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人  真的往這裡來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  有目擊情報說走過這個天橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這前面有什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩天輪和港口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是個難得的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然和計程車的隊伍搞錯  排到摩天輪的隊伍去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  風景真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  戒指在我這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能聽到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  請快點讓我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  是最高級的金華火腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快停下來啊  店都亂套了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣根本做不了生意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商品的損失  你要賠償
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  就算你這麼對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不好了  目標往港口去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  沒工夫在這瞎耗了  快追快追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那邊好像發生什麼事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在啊  去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓  我馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把戒指奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快賠錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你對我這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種金額的支票  我受不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請一定接受肉包子的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫  請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  戒指  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這附近和想像的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那麼開始佈置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  戒指  戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  梓  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒指在我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丟失的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  吶  攝影師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  絕對要拍下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…來送戒指的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒了它  你一定很為難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物歸原主了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你們的主人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種戒指  給我都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是  太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石油王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  居然是這種超級帥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面  我是石油王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的求婚  我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來  你的占卜很準啊  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真  這演的是哪出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…我也一頭霧水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真  製作人  來接我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  梓  平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的拍攝  還趕得上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然可以了  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的照片  已經拍下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  登載了登載了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個雜誌  因為這張照片而大受好評哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷地增印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:22:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓和龍宮小町的知名度也是一下子提高了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也登載了很多美希和真的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  看啊  這個真非常帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中華街的修理費  都是石油王出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因為一半是他們的原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友美發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(70,20)\fs18}「告訴你一個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(40,40)\fs18}那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(110,60)\fs18}聽說沒有婚約卻穿了婚紗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(63,80)\fs18}婚期會延遲哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說沒有婚約卻穿了婚紗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚期會延遲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾啊  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週的偶像大師
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水瀨伊織
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家全都是幸運兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為每週都能看到伊織的漂亮臉蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.39,0:24:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以下週也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.60,0:24:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好期待吧
